{"tid":2079711,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"討論「借錢比人」","createTime":"2020-06-26T03:23:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-26T03:54:32.000Z","uid":360231,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"243058fc71221db6a7470c303760fc77fe486617","tid":2079711,"uid":360231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T03:23:06.000Z","msg":"如果屋企人/朋友問你借錢你借唔借？<br />\n<br />\n我自己就覺得要假設對方唔會還比你，如果你預左收唔返但都願意既就借啦。"},{"pid":"ef21955acd49cbf86b04253599583b0bb1006f89","tid":2079711,"uid":72863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T03:26:14.000Z","msg":"召喚阿偉"},{"pid":"bbab159ab4218f232ed27ed825aaa3998acef72a","tid":2079711,"uid":87973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T03:28:06.000Z","msg":"如果佢信貸好 我會講<br />\n借定唔借 還得到先好借<br />\n<br />\n如果佢信貸無咁好 我會講<br />\n借錢梗要還 咪俾錢中介<br />\n<br />\n如果佢信貸唔好 佢唔會搵到我"},{"pid":"a38e99017cf860bb672a41aa4082364afea18ce5","tid":2079711,"uid":308795,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T03:28:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BumevxA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBumevxA.jpg&h=90d749ee&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c83b57a9e729a66bfc3725d3f1701c1908a67466","tid":2079711,"uid":75448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T03:30:16.000Z","msg":"想幫佢就唔好借比佢，<br />\n真係覺得佢好困難就當捐錢咁畀你比得起的錢佢應急，破產都要比手續費架嘛。"},{"pid":"6600bf9587e8ff071b0c0fc97552a826028cdf57","tid":2079711,"uid":252985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T03:30:23.000Z","msg":"😦😦😦"},{"pid":"43b80c2751bc064ab1d8ee5bb3d47af4e11d3d87","tid":2079711,"uid":238415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T03:30:55.000Z","msg":"計息咪借...同簽借據"},{"pid":"c1591ff5b84a210e9a3f7b3aae9857b69e43cbc5","tid":2079711,"uid":16956,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T03:31:41.000Z","msg":"追人還錢慘過狗"},{"pid":"b8d333b4a74f3b7e1c9fd74c8723f7e3e6a5b9f6","tid":2079711,"uid":159234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T03:32:00.000Z","msg":"never"},{"pid":"5ff385ac9fcc8fd1acaf94d6aae650214845f34e","tid":2079711,"uid":132810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T03:32:23.000Z","msg":"有能力，會，但都可能預左對方唔還。"},{"pid":"ec8c0f5bb431eb1624d71aed76c35d181f3d2e7d","tid":2079711,"uid":7332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T03:32:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"216d8778112147a8e58c2fb64e549f3ca3a23705","tid":2079711,"uid":205043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T03:33:03.000Z","msg":"借錢如送禮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01ccb027f3eee32f30a851c400fc07aad05a674f","tid":2079711,"uid":2772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T03:33:23.000Z","msg":"睇下借黎做乜<br />\n佢有機會搵得返 先會還錢俾你<br />\n唔係就唔洗攪到要借錢<br />\n<br />\n做生意周轉咪借<br />\n<br />\n幫人填氹/賭/洗大左就唔借"},{"pid":"fb1e910fbcecc99f822a6244150631726a4cd8a7","tid":2079711,"uid":24570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a38e99017cf860bb672a41aa4082364afea18ce5","tid":2079711,"uid":308795,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T03:28:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BumevxA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBumevxA.jpg&h=90d749ee&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T03:33:37.000Z","msg":"☺️"},{"pid":"ab38022b2c0c4671811b54595d593ce9c2c1fc04","tid":2079711,"uid":252985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"43b80c2751bc064ab1d8ee5bb3d47af4e11d3d87","tid":2079711,"uid":238415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T03:30:55.000Z","msg":"計息咪借...同簽借據"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T03:38:28.000Z","msg":"都無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申 試過 老死"},{"pid":"e99ea293316eb8